summary: Pedagogy expert, linguist, teacher and Teach For Australia alum. Passionate about  inclusive education for all regardless of postcode and background, and developing curricula that engage higher-order-thinking skills in learners.  Bilingual English/ Persian, comfortable in French and learning Dutch. Ardent football fan, yogi and hiker.
